    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introduction to docutils</title>

      <para>
        <application>docutils</application> is a set of
        <application>Python</application> modules and programs
        for processing plaintext docs into formats such as HTML, XML, or LaTeX.
      </para>

      &lfs122_checked;

